window.bookSummaryJSON = "Wallace D. Wattles was an American \"New Thought\" writer who wrote this amazing little book in 1910. It caused a sensation then, and continues to be popular today. In fact, Rhonda Byrne said that part of her inspriation for her best-selling book and film <i>The Secret</i> came from this book."; 
